actionConfiguration.body:
() => {
			const retain_keyPersonData = appsmith.store.keyPersonData
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_TYPE  = ''
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_IS_AUTH_SIGN = false
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_OTHERS_INFO = ''
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_PARTNER_PERC = Number(0).toString()
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_FIRSTNAME = Input1.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_MIDDLENAME = Input3.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_LASTNAME = Input4.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_MOTHERNAME  = Input5.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_FATHERNAME = Input6.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_DOB = moment(DatePicker1).format("YYYY-MM-DD")
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_TAX_ID  = Input7.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_NATIONALITY = Select3.selectedOptionValue
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_RES_TAX_PURPOSE = ''
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_DESIGNATION  = ''
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_PASSPORT_NO = Input19.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_PASSPORT_EXPIRE_DATE = moment(DatePicker1).format("YYYY-MM-DD")
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ACCESS_AS = vayEntityAdminUserAccess.selectedOptionValue
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_DIN_DPIN  = ''
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_LINE1  = Input9.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_LINE2  = Input10.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_CITY  = Input11.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_DISTRICT  = Input12.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_STATE  = Input13.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_COUNTRY = vayIndEaAddCountrySelect.selectedOptionValue
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_ZIP = Input15.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_MOBILE  = Input16.text
			retain_keyPersonData[0].CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_EMAIL   = Input17.text
		  appsmith.store.vayCCY.map((item) =>{
				 return ({
							CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_CURRENCY_CODE_FORADMTXN:item,
							CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_CURRENCY_LIMIT:Input18.text
				});
	  	});
		return retain_keyPersonData
	}
